parameters: Please help me won't you? My son! He's gone
Missing? What happened? Try to calm down if
you can, every detail is important Nerys.
He...he went out exploring with his friends.
I think he went to the White Tower south of
here - but he knows better than that! It's
haunted and he knows not to go there!
Ok - what's his name? And his friend's names?
Did any of them come back from this tower?
His name is Julian. His friends are Morn and
Miles. Miles came back to tell us about the
tower, but he ran off again!
Don't the clockwork knights ever come out to
this part of the realm? Can't they help you?
They almost never come by here anymore. There's
something else going on near the city just now.
Please, I have no one else to turn to!
Elim, we can't stop to help everyone who might
need it. It's unfortunate, but time is against
The dragonkin speaks sense Elim - we can't
It's not just about time, it's about allies. If
we want the people of Durast to stand with us
when the time comes, we need to be willing to
Nice to see that having a brush with Sargon
didn't make you forget yourself Elim.
His time will come. For now, yes Nerys, we will
help find your son. Can you tell me more about
Take the trail from the south exit of the
village, you can't miss it. Legend says that
it's the tomb of a former ruler of Garras,
but no one ever goes there anymore. It is said
that the spirits of the damned are cursed to
reside there - but no one is supposed to go
We will get to the bottom of this. But I want
to be frank with you - you have to be prepared
for the worst. We will do all in our power to
bring him back, but be ready for anything, ok?
...thank you, that's all I can ask.
Go home for now - we will come back to see you
when we have checked the tomb.
